    org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.IDialogPage, org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.IMessageProvider, org.eclipse.jface.wizard.IWizardPage

    public class NewScriptFileWizardPage
extends org.eclipse.jface.wizard.WizardPage

    The "New" wizard page allows setting the container for the new file as well as the file name. The page will only accept file name without the extension OR with the extension that matches the expected one (mqsc).
